        <h3>How do I set a filter?</h3>
        <p>Simply append a hash tag to the url: <b>http://trelloactivity.apphb.com/#displayActivityBoard</b>. Then add that tag to the description of the board. You can add the text anywhere, e.g. "#displayActivityBoard" and "@@#displayActivityBoard" will both work.</p>
